---
description: Restart blissful-soul Docker dev stack after config or dependency changes
globs:
  - blissful-soul/next.config.*
  - blissful-soul/.env*
  - blissful-soul/docker-compose*.yml
  - blissful-soul/Dockerfile*
  - blissful-soul/prisma/seed.ts
  - blissful-soul/prisma/schema.prisma
---

After editing Next config, env files, Docker Compose, Prisma schema/seed, or anything that affects the running app or DB container, restart the dev containers so changes apply:

```powershell
Set-Location "e:\Projects\New folder\blissful-soul"; .\restart-dev-docker.ps1
```

Or run:

```powershell
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.dev.yml restart db app
```

Do this automatically after such edits unless the user explicitly asks not to.
